trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.WebReferenceOptions" /> class represents code generation options specified in an XML text file.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.WebReferenceOptions" /> 類別表示 XML 文字檔中指定的程式碼產生選項。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.WebReferenceOptions" />.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.WebReferenceOptions" /> 的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <see cref="T:System.Xml.Serialization.CodeGenerationOptions" /> associated with this <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.WebReferenceOptions" />.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定與這個 <see cref="T:System.Xml.Serialization.CodeGenerationOptions" /> 關聯的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.WebReferenceOptions" />。

trans-unit.source: Returns a new instance of <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.WebReferenceOptions" /> based on the code generation options described in the specified input.
trans-unit.target: 根據指定輸入中所描述的程式碼產生選項，傳回 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.WebReferenceOptions" /> 的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a <see cref="T:System.Boolean" /> value that indicates whether verbose warning messages are to be generated during compilation of a client proxy or a server stub.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定 <see cref="T:System.Boolean" /> 值，指出在編譯用戶端 Proxy 或伺服器 Stub 期間，是否會產生詳細警告訊息。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if verbose warning messages are to be generated during compilation of a client proxy or a server stub; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果在編譯用戶端 Proxy 或伺服器 Stub 期間會產生詳細警告訊息，則為 <see langword="true" />，否則為 <see langword="false" />。
